            ['id' => 38, 'product_category_id' => 29, 'name' => 'Farmhouse Cross Back Bar Stool - Limewash', 'slug' => 'farmhouse-cross-back-bar-stool-limewash', 'sku' => 'XBBS55LW', 'brand' => 'Titan Event Furniture™', 'price' => 102.99, 'stock' => 100, 'image' => 'images/products/farmhouse-cross-back-bar-stool-limewash/4d47311d218a.jpg', 'gallery' => '["images\\/products\\/farmhouse-cross-back-bar-stool-limewash\\/4d47311d218a.jpg","images\\/products\\/farmhouse-cross-back-bar-stool-limewash\\/d77b24359028.jpg","images\\/products\\/farmhouse-cross-back-bar-stool-limewash\\/3537cf62fe18.jpg","images\\/products\\/farmhouse-cross-back-bar-stool-limewash\\/ee7e0e25e073.jpg","images\\/products\\/farmhouse-cross-back-bar-stool-limewash\\/828f88a71a50.jpg"]', 'description' => 'The Farmhouse Cross Back Bar Stool from EventStable offers a perfect blend of rustic charm and practical elegance, making it an ideal choice for event venues, restaurants, and everyday spaces.', 'features' => '["The Farmhouse Cross Back Bar Stool from EventStable offers a perfect blend of rustic charm and practical elegance, making it an ideal choice for event venues, restaurants, and everyday spaces.","Crafted from high-quality beechwood, this commercial-grade bar stool features a beautifully curved cross-back design, providing not only timeless visual appeal but also sturdy support.","The lightly distressed finish enhances its farmhouse aesthetic, giving each piece unique character.","With a comfortable 30\'\' seat height, this seating option is perfect for bar counters, cocktail tables or other high-top dining, while adding a welcoming touch to any setting.","Its versatile style complements a wide range of d\\u00e9cor, from rustic and vintage-inspired venues to modern, laid-back spaces.","Designed for both durability and comfort, the farmhouse cross back bar stool is built to withstand the demands of frequent use while maintaining its charm."]', 'specifications' => '{"Free Shipping Deal Type":"F