            ['id' => 49, 'product_category_id' => 29, 'name' => 'Madison Cross Back Chair - Mark II - Fruitwood', 'slug' => 'madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood', 'sku' => 'XBC45FW', 'brand' => 'Titan Event Furniture™', 'price' => 62.99, 'stock' => 100, 'image' => 'images/products/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood/1aa6fe4b5378.jpg', 'gallery' => '["images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/1aa6fe4b5378.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/b3d986831192.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/74c8dd47bca7.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/36fafeb388ec.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/4dc3b714366d.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/042eb87c0130.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/31591708e8ad.jpg"]', 'description' => 'The New Madison Cross Back Chair - Mark II features a stronger, handcrafted rubber wood frame for commercial use.', 'features' => '["The New Madison Cross Back Chair - Mark II features a stronger, handcrafted rubber wood frame for commercial use.","This stackable chair is built for indoor and outdoor events and ships fully assembled.","If you preferred the original Madison Cross Back Chairs because of the comfortably wider 16.5\'\' seat, do not fret.","Our new Mark II Madison Cross Back Chairs bring back everything you loved in the previous model and improved on it.","The sturdy rubber wood construction has been replaced by a more durable, hand crafted frame that\'s better built for sustained commercial use, whether it be an indoor wedding ceremony or an outdoor anniversary party.","Madison Cross Back Chairs are available in Fruitwood, Antique Fruitwood and Pecan and don\'t forget to add a seat cushion for added comfort.","As always, these chairs ship free when you puy 50+ or combine them with tables, like our Folding Farm Table!If you appreciated the durability and classic appeal of commercial-grade seating, the Titan Event Furniture\\u2122 Rubber Wood Chair is a perfect fit.","Constructed from solid rubber wood, this chair is built to handle the demands of event venues, restaurants, and rental use.","With an overall height of 35.5\\u2019\\u2019 and an 18\\u2019\\u2019 seat height, it provides a comfortable sitting experience, while the 16\\" x 15.5\\" seat ensures ample space.","Despite its sturdy build, this chair remains lightweight at just 10 lbs. and is fully stackable for easy storage.","With a static weight capacity of 400 lbs. and a dynamic weight capacity of 300 lbs., it offers reliable support in any setting.","Best of all, these chairs ship fully assembled, and ship free when you buy 50+ or combine them with any purchase over $5k!"]', 'specifications' => '{"Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k, Free Shipping on 50 or more","Can ship FedEx?":"Yes","Country of Manufacture":"Vietnam","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Material":"Rubber Wood","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Overall Height":"35.5\'\'","Overall Width":"18\'\'","Seat Height":"18\'\'","Seat Size":"16\\" W x 15.5\\" D","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Stackable?":"Yes","Has Arms":"No","Item Weight":"10 lbs.","Static Weight Capacity":"400 lbs.","Dynamic Weight Capacity":"300 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[{"question":"Will I be able to stack my Cross Back Chairs","answer":"Yes, all of our Cross Back Chairs are stackable. We generally stack them 7 chairs high on the floor, on pallets or on one of our stacking chair dollies."},{"question":"What is Rubber Wood?","answer":"Rubber wood comes from the Par\\u00e1 rubber tree and is a durable, eco-friendly hardwood. It\'s strong, resistant to warping, and has a smooth grain, making it ideal for commercial furniture like cross back chairs."},{"question":"Are Madison Cross Back Chairs suitable for outdoor use?","answer":"Yes! Madison Cross Back Chairs are designed for both indoor and outdoor use. Their durable rubber wood construction makes them a great choice for event venues, restaurants, and rental setups. However, to extend their lifespan, it\'s best to store them indoors or in a covered area when not in use"}]', 'default_color' => 'Fruitwood', 'color_variants' => '[{"label":"Fruitwood","swatch":"images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/8119f3ade5d7.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/7d11c97ca623.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/e24512818ff1.png"]},{"label":"Antique Fruitwood","swatch":"images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/3562e5e9338b.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/0597bb7da85e.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/926dc0ab7aca.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/20d7e52fa4a8.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/65cf74199431.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/07a5d3cc1f4e.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/4153b43617b3.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/3340f31978d2.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/c606d2855ecd.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/1205d99dea95.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/69d93dda8af5.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/f679a3433d74.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/24e98ff2362b.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/3c671a2cd2c8.jpg","images\\/products\\/madison-cross-back-chair-mark-ii-fruitwood\\/e3b11d203176.jpg"]}]', 'is_active' => 1, 'created_at' => '2026-06-18 04:21:51', 'updated_at' => '2026-06-18 11:38:01'],
            ['id' => 50, 'product_category_id' => 29, 'name' => 'Outdoor Dining Bundle with Madison Cross Back Chairs', 'slug' => 'outdoor-dining-bundle-with-madison-cross-back-chairs', 'sku' => 'ODBDL-XBC45', 'brand' => 'Titan Event Furniture™', 'price' => 5609.83, 'stock' => 100, 'image' => 'images/products/outdoor-dining-bundle-with-madison-cross-back-chairs/12301047201d.png', 'gallery' => '["images\\/products\\/outdoor-dining-bundle-with-madison-cross-back-chairs\\/12301047201d.png","images\\/products\\/outdoor-dining-bundle-with-madison-cross-back-chairs\\/b515ef4cad6d.jpg"]', 'description' => 'Move your dining room to the fresh air with our Outdoor Dining Bundle featuring 24 of our Madison Cross Back Chair - Mark II.', 'features' => '["Move your dining room to the fresh air with our Outdoor Dining Bundle featuring 24 of our Madison Cross Back Chair - Mark II.","Whether you live where it\'s summer all the time or you only get to cherish 5 months of sunshine bliss, this package is the one stop shop to turn your restaurant, bistro, cafe, pub or winery into an outside oasis.","Both of our 48\'\' Round Titan Series Wood Folding Table and our 48\'\' x 48\'\' Square Titan Series Wood Folding Table will comfortable seat 4-6 guests with room to spare so you can sit comfortably and still maintain 6 feet from your fellow diners.","If you really want to take your dining performance up a notch, Choose our 48\'\' Round TitanPRO\\u2122 Heavy Duty Wood Folding Table with metal edge, our most durable line of wooden banquet folding tables.","With warmer months comes unpredictable weather.","So you\'re always prepared for rain or a little too much shine, our UV resistant 20\' x 20\' Cross Cable Tent is included to take of that and more.","Sidewalls for the tent are also option if you so choose."]', 'specifications' => '{"Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping, Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k","Can ship FedEx?":"Yes","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Commercial-Grade?":"No","Ships Assembled?":"No","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[]', 'default_color' => NULL, 'color_variants' => '[]', 'is_active' => 1, 'created_at' => '2026-06-18 04:21:52', 'updated_at' => '2026-06-18 11:38:01'],
            ['id' => 51, 'product_category_id' => 38, 'name' => 'Sonoma Oak Cross Back Chair - Marian Fruitwood - Closeout', 'slug' => 'sonoma-oak-cross-back-chair-marian-fruitwood-closeout', 'sku' => 'SXBC-C4-MFW', 'brand' => 'CSP', 'price' => 80.49, 'stock' => 100, 'image' => 'images/products/sonoma-oak-cross-back-chair-marian-fruitwood-closeout/1bac3c25fdeb.jpg', 'gallery' => '["images\\/products\\/sonoma-oak-cross-back-chair-marian-fruitwood-closeout\\/1bac3c25fdeb.jpg","images\\/products\\/sonoma-oak-cross-back-chair-marian-fruitwood-closeout\\/24a0190927ec.jpg","images\\/products\\/sonoma-oak-cross-back-chair-marian-fruitwood-closeout\\/972c09d3ce48.jpg","images\\/products\\/sonoma-oak-cross-back-chair-marian-fruitwood-closeout\\/9216ed487ce8.jpg","images\\/products\\/sonoma-oak-cross-back-chair-marian-fruitwood-closeout\\/83a7c6d7b990.png","images\\/products\\/sonoma-oak-cross-back-chair-marian-fruitwood-closeout\\/ce50dee5adc7.png","images\\/products\\/sonoma-oak-cross-back-chair-marian-fruitwood-closeout\\/60ecabbb5fa0.png"]', 'description' => 'Sonoma Oak Cross Back Bar Stools also available - See them here', 'features' => '["Sonoma Oak Cross Back Bar Stools also available - See them here","The Sonoma Cross Back Chair invites a sense of timeless heritage into your space, bridging the gap between rugged farmhouse charm and sophisticated elegance.","Carved from genuine solid hardwood oak, each piece serves as a testament to natural beauty, featuring a weathered antique finish that highlights the unique character of the wood grain.","This chair is not merely a seat but a design statement, offering an inviting warmth that transforms any indoor dining environment into a curated experience.","Beyond its aesthetic appeal, the Sonoma is engineered for the high-energy demands of commercial hospitality.","The signature cross-back silhouette is thoughtfully contoured to provide ergonomic support, ensuring that guests remain comfortable from the first course to the final toast.","While the design looks delicate and historic, the solid oak construction provides a sturdy, dependable foundation built to endure years of consistent use.","Functionality remains at the heart of the Sonoma design, particularly for venues that require frequent transitions.","These chairs stack seamlessly up to eight high, allowing for effortless reconfiguration and compact storage when the floor needs to be cleared.","By combining the soul of traditional craftsmanship with the practical needs of modern event management, the Sonoma Cross Back Chair offers a durable, space-saving solution that never compromises on style."]', 'specifications' => '{"Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k, Free Shipping on 50 or more","Can ship FedEx?":"Yes","Brand":"CSP","Material":"Elm Wood","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Overall Height":"35\'\'","Overall Width":"17.5\'\'","Overall Length \\/ Depth":"16.25\'\'","Seat Height":"18\'\'","Seat Material":"Oak Wood","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Stackable?":"Yes","Has Arms":"No","Item Weight":"11 lbs.","Weight Capacity":"500 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[]', 'default_color' => 'Marian Fruitwood', 'color_variants' => '[{"label":"Dark Walnut","swatch":"images\\/products\\/sonoma-oak-cross-back-chair-marian-fruitwood-closeout\\/f99d22291756.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/sonoma-oak-cross-back-chair-marian-fruitwood-closeout\\/292ff677d54f.png","images\\/products\\/sonoma-oak-cross-back-chair-marian-fruitwood-closeout\\/41c8c744a0aa.png","images\\/products\\/sonoma-oak-cross-back-chair-marian-fruitwood-closeout\\/dfa1e17c0782.png","images\\/products\\/sonoma-oak-cross-back-chair-marian-fruitwood-closeout\\/a3a5e3794b81.png","images\\/products\\/sonoma-oak-cross-back-chair-marian-fruitwood-closeout\\/b6fd4a8391cf.png","images\\/products\\/sonoma-oak-cross-back-chair-marian-fruitwood-closeout\\/206005730114.png","images\\/products\\/sonoma-oak-cross-back-c