ch seat height is ideal for various table settings, ensuring your guests are seated comfortably throughout the event.","Arriving fully assembled and stackable, each chair offers unparalleled convenience for event organizers.","Whether you\'re hosting a wedding, corporate function, or any special gathering, the ease of setup and storage makes this chair a go-to choice.","With a remarkable weight capacity of 500 lbs. and a lightweight design at just 15 lbs., these chairs effortlessly blend functionality and style, making them a must-have for any event where comfort and elegance are paramount.","Elevate your event experience with the TitanPRO\\u2122 Crown Back Banquet Chair \\u2013 where durability meets sophistication, setting the stage for unforgettable moments.","Best of all, these stacking chairs ship free when you purchase 50+ or combine them in an order with other equipment over $5k!"]', 'specifications' => '{"Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k, Free Shipping on 50 or more","Can ship FedEx?":"Yes","Country of Manufacture":"China","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Back Style":"Crown Back","Frame Color":"Silver Vein Frame","Upholstery Type":"Vinyl","Material":"Stainless 18\\/10 Heavy Gauge","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Overall Height":"37\'\'","Overall Width":"17.5\'\'","Overall Length \\/ Depth":"21\'\'","Seat Height":"19\'\'","Seat Material":"Vinyl","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Stackable?":"Yes","Weight Capacity":"500 lbs.","Item Weight":"15 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[]', 'default_color' => 'Black Vinyl', 'color_variants' => '[{"label":"Black Vinyl","swatch":"images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-silver-vein-frame-black-vinyl\\/95684125beea.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-silver-vein-frame-black-vinyl\\/b4b32ac7f974.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-silver-vein-frame-black-vinyl\\/04db1b0a40a2.jpg","images\\/products\\/