'","Seat Size":"15.7\'\' x 15.4\'\'","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Stackable?":"Yes","Item Weight":"12 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[]', 'default_color' => NULL, 'color_variants' => '[]', 'is_active' => 1, 'created_at' => '2026-06-18 08:10:36', 'updated_at' => '2026-06-18 08:38:17'],
            ['id' => 87, 'product_category_id' => 31, 'name' => 'Crown Back Banquet Chair - Gold Frame - Burgundy Fabric with Gold Dot Pattern', 'slug' => 'crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern', 'sku' => 'CBC9BGFGD', 'brand' => 'Titan Event Furniture™', 'price' => 42.49, 'stock' => 100, 'image' => 'images/products/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern/ed344075f558.jpg', 'gallery' => '["images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/ed344075f558.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/b41537c37c0e.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/42036d2bea75.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/7dcfd3d5c560.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/352537dfb5cf.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/769a01291ef8.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/80a7bb3713b5.png"]', 'description' => 'The TitanPRO™ Crown Back Banquet Chair with Gold Frame is built for banquet halls, hotel ballrooms, wedding venues, and event rental operations that need a stackable chair with a formal aesthetic and commercial durability.', 'features' => '["The TitanPRO\\u2122 Crown Back Banquet Chair with Gold Frame is built for banquet halls, hotel ballrooms, wedding venues, and event rental operations that need a stackable chair with a formal aesthetic and commercial durability.","The 18-gauge steel frame with gold finish supports 500+ lbs., stacks for efficient storage, and pairs with a commercial-grade polyurethane foam seat cushion available in multiple fabric patterns to match your venue\'s style.","At 15 lbs. and 37\\" tall with a 19\\" seat height, it fits standard banquet table heights and ships fully assembled.","Gold frame finish adds formal presence without added maintenance. The powder-coated gold steel frame delivers a ballroom-ready aesthetic across a full inventory and resists chipping and wear through regular commercial use better than painted finishes.","Commercial-grade foam seat holds up through high-frequency use. The polyurethane foam cushion is built to maintain its shape and firmness over time, so chairs that are set up and broken down multiple times per week continue to provide consistent guest comfort rather than flattening out.","Multiple fabric patterns let you match your venue\'s d\\u00e9cor. Available in a range of upholstery options, these chairs can be configured to complement your existing color scheme or build a consistent look across your entire banquet chair inventory.","Crown back design supports guests through longer seated events. The shaped crown back provides more upper and lower back contact than a flat back panel, reducing discomfort for guests during multi-hour dinners, conferences, and ceremonies.","Stacks and ships assembled for efficient operations. Chairs arrive ready to use with no assembly required, and the stackable design minimizes floor space in storage and simplifies loading and unloading for rental deliveries."]', 'specifications' => '{"Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k, Free Shipping on 50 or more","Can ship FedEx?":"Yes","Country of Manufacture":"China","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Overall Height":"37\'\'","Overall Width":"17.5\'\'","Overall Length \\/ Depth":"21\'\'","Seat Height":"19\'\'","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Back Style":"Crown Back","Stackable?":"Yes","Frame Color":"Gold Frame","Has Arms":"No","Product Warranty":"1 Year Warranty","Item Weight":"15 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[{"question":"What is a crown back banquet chair?","answer":"A crown back banquet chair is a stacking chair with a back panel shaped in a gentle arch or crown silhouette, as opposed to a flat rectangular back. The shape is a staple in formal event settings \\u2014 hotel ballrooms, banquet halls, and wedding venues \\u2014 because it reads as more polished than a standard flat-back chair while still being stackable and practical for commercial operations."},{"question":"What is the weight capacity of this chair?","answer":"The TitanPRO\\u2122 Crown Back Banquet Chair is rated for 500+ lbs. of static weight capacity. See the specs tab for the full breakdown of static vs. dynamic weight ratings."},{"question":"What is the seat height and does it fit standard banquet tables?","answer":"The seat height is 19\\", which fits standard 30\\" banquet tables with appropriate legroom for most adult guests. The overall chair height is 37\\"."},{"question":"How many chairs stack for storage?","answer":"Crown Back Banquet Chairs stack 10 to 12 high, making them efficient to store and transport in a warehouse or cargo area. For operations moving large quantities, EventStable carries compatible stacking chair dollies to simplify bulk handling between events."}]', 'default_color' => 'Burgundy Patterned', 'color_variants' => '[{"label":"Black Pattern","swatch":"images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/e7d46e041e72.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/4af049d7121f.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/916d410a793f.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/347c26f75111.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/48564333d114.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/974bd1dc6aa0.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/769a01291ef8.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/80a7bb3713b5.png"]},{"label":"Burgundy Patterned","swatch":"images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/e0d23cb56f80.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/ed344075f558.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/b41537c37c0e.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/42036d2bea75.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/7dcfd3d5c560.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/352537dfb5cf.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/769a01291ef8.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/80a7bb3713b5.png"]},{"label":"Navy Blue Patterned","swatch":"images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/e81455910d20.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/924589a082a6.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/a5c389100cdc.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/67dcf4a71d4b.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/582ec65358e5.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/a20888c84018.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/e0abd0fc2151.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-burgundy-fabric-with-gold-dot-pattern\\/f67694204476.jpg"]}]', 'is_active' => 1, 'created_at' => '2026-06-18 08:10:45', 'updated_at' => '2026-06-18 08:38:17'],
