            ['id' => 89, 'product_category_id' => 31, 'name' => 'Crown Back Banquet Chair - Gold Frame - Navy Blue Patterned', 'slug' => 'crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned', 'sku' => 'CBC9NVFGF-BD', 'brand' => 'Titan Event Furniture™', 'price' => 42.49, 'stock' => 100, 'image' => 'images/products/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned/924589a082a6.jpg', 'gallery' => '["images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/924589a082a6.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/a5c389100cdc.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/67dcf4a71d4b.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/582ec65358e5.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/a20888c84018.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/e0abd0fc2151.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/f67694204476.jpg"]', 'description' => 'The TitanPRO™ Crown Back Banquet Chair with Gold Frame is built for banquet halls, hotel ballrooms, wedding venues, and event rental operations that need a stackable chair with a formal aesthetic and commercial durability.', 'features' => '["The TitanPRO\\u2122 Crown Back Banquet Chair with Gold Frame is built for banquet halls, hotel ballrooms, wedding venues, and event rental operations that need a stackable chair with a formal aesthetic and commercial durability.","The 18-gauge steel frame with gold finish supports 500+ lbs., stacks for efficient storage, and pairs with a commercial-grade polyurethane foam seat cushion available in multiple fabric patterns to match your venue\'s style.","At 15 lbs. and 37\\" tall with a 19\\" seat height, it fits standard banquet table heights and ships fully assembled.","Gold frame finish adds formal presence without added maintenance. The powder-coated gold steel frame delivers a ballroom-ready aesthetic across a full inventory and resists chipping and wear through regular commercial use better than painted finishes.","Commercial-grade foam seat holds up through high-frequency use. The polyurethane foam cushion is built to maintain its shape and firmness over time, so chairs that are set up and broken down multiple times per week continue to provide consistent guest comfort rather than flattening out.","Multiple fabric patterns let you match your venue\'s d\\u00e9cor. Available in a range of upholstery options, these chairs can be configured to complement your existing color scheme or build a consistent look across your entire banquet chair inventory.","Crown back design supports guests through longer seated events. The shaped crown back provides more upper and lower back contact than a flat back panel, reducing discomfort for guests during multi-hour dinners, conferences, and ceremonies.","Stacks and ships assembled for efficient operations. Chairs arrive ready to use with no assembly required, and the stackable design minimizes floor space in storage and simplifies loading and unloading for rental deliveries."]', 'specifications' => '{"Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k, Free Shipping on 50 or more","Can ship FedEx?":"Yes","Country of Manufacture":"China","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Overall Height":"37\'\'","Overall Width":"17.5\'\'","Overall Length \\/ Depth":"21\'\'","Seat Height":"19\'\'","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Back Style":"Crown Back","Stackable?":"Yes","Frame Color":"Gold Frame","Has Arms":"No","Product Warranty":"1 Year Warranty","Item Weight":"15 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[{"question":"What is a crown back banquet chair?","answer":"A crown back banquet chair is a stacking chair with a back panel shaped in a gentle arch or crown silhouette, as opposed to a flat rectangular back. The shape is a staple in formal event settings \\u2014 hotel ballrooms, banquet halls, and wedding venues \\u2014 because it reads as more polished than a standard flat-back chair while still being stackable and practical for commercial operations."},{"question":"What is the weight capacity of this chair?","answer":"The TitanPRO\\u2122 Crown Back Banquet Chair is rated for 500+ lbs. of static weight capacity. See the specs tab for the full breakdown of static vs. dynamic weight ratings."},{"question":"What is the seat height and does it fit standard banquet tables?","answer":"The seat height is 19\\", which fits standard 30\\" banquet tables with appropriate legroom for most adult guests. The overall chair height is 37\\"."},{"question":"How many chairs stack for storage?","answer":"Crown Back Banquet Chairs stack 10 to 12 high, making them efficient to store and transport in a warehouse or cargo area. For operations moving large quantities, EventStable carries compatible stacking chair dollies to simplify bulk handling between events."}]', 'default_color' => 'Navy Blue Patterned', 'color_variants' => '[{"label":"Black Pattern","swatch":"images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/e7d46e041e72.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/4af049d7121f.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/916d410a793f.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/347c26f75111.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/48564333d114.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/974bd1dc6aa0.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/769a01291ef8.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/80a7bb3713b5.png"]},{"label":"Burgundy Patterned","swatch":"images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/e0d23cb56f80.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/ed344075f558.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/b41537c37c0e.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/42036d2bea75.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/7dcfd3d5c560.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/352537dfb5cf.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/769a01291ef8.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/80a7bb3713b5.png"]},{"label":"Navy Blue Patterned","swatch":"images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/e81455910d20.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/924589a082a6.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/a5c389100cdc.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/67dcf4a71d4b.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/582ec65358e5.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/a20888c84018.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/e0abd0fc2151.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-gold-frame-navy-blue-patterned\\/f67694204476.jpg"]}]', 'is_active' => 1, 'created_at' => '2026-06-18 08:11:11', 'updated_at' => '2026-06-18 08:38:17'],
            ['id' => 90, 'product_category_id' => 31, 'name' => 'Crown Back Banquet Chair - Silver Vein Frame - Navy Vinyl', 'slug' => 'crown-back-banquet-chair-silver-vein-frame-navy-vinyl', 'sku' => 'CBC9NVSLVF-VNL', 'brand' => 'Titan Event Furniture™', 'price' => 42.49, 'stock' => 100, 'image' => 'images/products/crown-back-banquet-chair-silver-vein-frame-navy-vinyl/2cd396be9518.jpg', 'gallery' => '["images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-silver-vein-frame-navy-vinyl\\/2cd396be9518.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-silver-vein-frame-navy-vinyl\\/8246b3f74fc6.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-silver-vein-frame-navy-vinyl\\/4eeeaea2c7fe.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-silver-vein-frame-navy-vinyl\\/a097757d684b.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-silver-vein-frame-navy-vinyl\\/7ebf13c760bd.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-silver-vein-frame-navy-vinyl\\/8082b4b7a261.jpeg"]', 'description' => 'Introducing the TitaPRO™ Crown Back Banquet Chair, a pinnacle of style, durability, and comfort for your special occasions.', 'features' => '["Introducing the TitaPRO\\u2122 Crown Back Banquet Chair, a pinnacle of style, durability, and comfort for your special occasions.","Crafted with a sleek Silver Vein Frame, this chair not only exudes sophistication but also boasts a robust 18 gauge steel construction, making it the definition of commercial-grade seating.","Constructed with meticulous attention to detail, this chair features a plush vinyl upholstery in Navy or Black and provides a luxurious seating experience while also ensuring easy maintenance for long-lasting use.","With an overall height of 37\'\', a width of 17.5\'\', and a depth of 21\', the TitanPRO\\u2122 Crown Back Banquet Chair from EventStable strikes the perfect balance between comfort and space efficiency.","The 19-inch seat height is ideal for various table settings, ensuring your guests are seated comfortably throughout the event.","Arriving fully assembled and stackable, each chair offers unparalleled convenience for event organizers.","Whether you\'re hosting a wedding, corporate function, or any special gathering, the ease of setup and storage makes this chair a go-to choice.","With a remarkable weight capacity of 500 lbs. and a lightweight design at just 15 lbs., these chairs effortlessly blend functionality and style, making them a must-have for any event where comfort and elegance are paramount.","Elevate your event experience with the TitanPRO\\u2122 Crown Back Banquet Chair \\u2013 where durability meets sophistication, setting the stage for unforgettable moments.","Best of all, these stacking chairs ship free when you purchase 50+ or combine them in an order with other equipment over $5k!"]', 'specifications' => '{"Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k, Free Shipping on 50 or more","Can ship FedEx?":"Yes","Country of Manufacture":"China","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Back Style":"Crown Back","Frame Color":"Silver Vein Frame","Upholstery Type":"Vinyl","Material":"Stainless 18\\/10 Heavy Gauge","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Overall Height":"37\'\'","Overall Width":"17.5\'\'","Overall Length \\/ Depth":"21\'\'","Seat Height":"19\'\'","Seat Material":"Vinyl","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Stackable?":"Yes","Weight Capacity":"500 lbs.","Item Weight":"15 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[]', 'default_color' => 'Navy', 'color_variants' => '[{"label":"Black Vinyl","swatch":"images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-silver-vein-frame-navy-vinyl\\/95684125beea.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-silver-vein-frame-navy-vinyl\\/b4b32ac7f974.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-silver-vein-frame-navy-vinyl\\/04db1b0a40a2.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-chair-silver-vein-frame-navy-vinyl\\/5b0958c7711e.jpg","images\\/products\\/crown-back-banquet-