rade 3\\/4\'\' plywood with vinyl bullnose edging.","Both the top and bottom are polyurethane coated to ensure a long life.","An aluminum coupler comes complete with screws to secure under the tabletop.","This houses the pole and completes the set with the included 28\'\' aluminum base.","A small amount of assembly is required.","The table knocks down for easy storage and transport."]', 'specifications' => '{"Special Order Item":"No","UPC":"850004346136","Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k, Free Shipping on 10 or more","Can ship FedEx?":"Yes","Country of Manufacture":"China","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Material":"Wood","Shape":"Round","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Overall Length \\/ Depth":"36\'\'","Overall Height":"30\'\', 42\'\'","Overall Width":"36\'\'","Recommended Seating":"3","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Product Warranty":"3 Years","Item Weight":"29","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[]', 'default_color' => NULL, 'color_variants' => '[]', 'is_active' => 1, 'created_at' => '2026-06-18 08:11:39', 'updated_at' => '2026-06-18 08:38:17'],
            ['id' => 103, 'product_category_id' => 18, 'name' => 'Cocktail Table Cart - for 24\'\' cocktail tables', 'slug' => 'cocktail-table-cart-for-24-cocktail-tables', 'sku' => 'CTC2624', 'brand' => 'Titan Event Furniture™', 'price' => 516.49, 'stock' => 100, 'image' => 'images/products/cocktail-table-cart-for-24-cocktail-tables/0094dacf70b8.jpg', 'gallery' => '["images\\/products\\/cocktail-table-cart-for-24-cocktail-tables\\/0094dacf70b8.jpg","images\\/products\\/cocktail-table-cart-for-24-cocktail-tables\\/0e1ac7617028.jpg","images\\/products\\/cocktail-table-cart-for-24-cocktail-tables\\/957feb05b117.jpeg"]', 'description' => 'Looking for a cart to hold cocktail tables?', 'features' => '["Looking for a cart to hold cocktail tables?","Look no further.","Cocktail table cart for use with our 24\'\' cocktail tables.","Holds 10 table sets.","Having been in the party rental business, we know how difficult it can be keeping track of the pieces for cocktail tables.","It takes forever to locate and carry the different components to set up for the next event.","Well, this is no longer a problem with our carts specifically designed to hold cocktail tables, belly bars, high boys, or whatever you call them.","Our cocktail table carts are built to hold everything you need to store and transport 10 cocktail tables.","Commercial-grade steel assembly assures strength and durability so you can focus on getting the event set up.","Just slide the tabletops in face-to-face, put the bases on the built-in poles on top, and slide the columns in the attached individual compartments.","Ships unassembled so some assembly is required.","Assembled dimensions: 28.5\'\'W x 24\'\'D x 79\'\'H"]', 'specifications' => '{"UPC":"850004346143","Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k","Can ship FedEx?":"No","Country of Manufacture":"China","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Cart Type":"Cocktail Table Cart","Overall Length \\/ Depth":"24\'\'","Overall Height":"79\'\'","Overall Width":"28.5\'\'","Ships Assembled?":"No","Item Weight":"107 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[]', 'default_color' => NULL, 'color_variants' => '[]', 'is_active' => 1, 'created_at' => '2026-06-18 08:11:40', 'updated_at' => '2026-06-18 08:38:17'],
