 our Farmhouse Cross Back Chairs.","Shop our collection of farm-style tables and stacking chairs, including Cross Back Chairs and Bentwood Chairs, and take advantage of our free shipping deals today!"]', 'specifications' => '{"Special Order Item":"No","Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k, Free Shipping on 10 or more","Can ship FedEx?":"Yes","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Shape":"Round","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Overall Length \\/ Depth":"60\'\'","Overall Height":"30\'\'","Overall Width":"60\'\'","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Item Weight":"99 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[]', 'default_color' => 'Black Grain on Antique Black', 'color_variants' => '[{"label":"Fruitwood with Black Grain","swatch":"#47260c","gallery":["images\\/products\\/farmhouse-60-round-folding-farm-table-black-grain-on-antique-black-h-legs\\/00cb087c9e2b.jpg","images\\/products\\/farmhouse-60-round-folding-farm-table-black-grain-on-antique-black-h-legs\\/ba8363c99055.jpg","images\\/products\\/farmhouse-60-round-folding-farm-table-black-grain-on-antique-black-h-legs\\/a0ad6e6eab3a.jpg","images\\/products\\/farmhouse-60-round-folding-farm-table-black-grain-on-antique-black-h-legs\\/808e847c53d4.jpg","images\\/products\\/farmhouse-60-round-folding-farm-table-black-grain-on-antique-black-h-legs\\/05e9d8bd2750.jpg","images\\/products\\/farmhouse-60-round-folding-farm-table-black-grain-on-antique-black-h-legs\\/028c296bb8aa.jpg","images\\/products\\/farmhouse-60-round-folding-farm-table-black-grain-on-antique-black-h-legs\\/59a2a081ccb7.jpg"]},{"label":"Black Grain on Antique Black","swatch":"images\\/products\\/farmhouse-60-round-folding-farm-table-black-grain-on-antique-black-h-legs\\/b44f4898a4f2.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/farmhouse-60-round-folding-farm-table-black-grain-on-antique-black-h-legs\\/18a802fa7807.jpg","images\\/products\\/farmhouse-60-round-folding-farm-table-black-grain-on-antique-black