y fold underneath when it\'s time pack up and move out.","Worried about pairing tables with event seating?","Don\'t fret!","Our Farmhouse Cross Back Chairs in either wood or commercial-grade resin were actually designed to match these farm tables exactly so you don\'t have to worry about mixing and matching from multiple vendors."]', 'specifications' => '{"Special Order Item":"No","Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k, Free Shipping on 10 or more","Can ship FedEx?":"No","Country of Manufacture":"China","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Material":"Pinewood","Shape":"Rectangle","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Overall Length \\/ Depth":"96\'\'","Overall Height":"30\'\'","Overall Width":"40\'\'","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Item Weight":"115 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[]', 'default_color' => 'Black Grain on Antique Black', 'color_variants' => '[{"label":"Fruitwood with Black Grain","swatch":"#47260c","gallery":["images\\/products\\/farmhouse-folding-farm-table-40-x-96-black-grain-on-antique-black-x-legs\\/b92c44fa6123.jpg","images\\/products\\/farmhouse-folding-farm-table-40-x-96-black-grain-on-antique-black-x-legs\\/1ce16980db2d.jpg","images\\/products\\/farmhouse-folding-farm-table-40-x-96-black-grain-on-antique-black-x-legs\\/1401c9f3ad5e.jpg","images\\/products\\/farmhouse-folding-farm-table-40-x-96-black-grain-on-antique-black-x-legs\\/ea693323615b.jpg","images\\/products\\/farmhouse-folding-farm-table-40-x-96-black-grain-on-antique-black-x-legs\\/33db6dcddcf3.jpg","images\\/products\\/farmhouse-folding-farm-table-40-x-96-black-grain-on-antique-black-x-legs\\/88970dcdae0c.png"]},{"label":"Black Grain on Antique Black","swatch":"images\\/products\\/farmhouse-folding-farm-table-40-x-96-black-grain-on-antique-black-x-legs\\/b44f4898a4f2.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/farmhouse-folding-farm-table-40-x-96-black-grain-on-antique-black-x-legs\\/7c1b4c9acce3.jpg","images\\/products\