storage. No tools, no assembly, no complexity \\u2014 the bench unfolds and is ready to use in seconds, and folds flat for efficient storage in a warehouse or trailer between events.","At 34 lbs., one person can move and set it efficiently. Light enough for a single crew member to handle across a full event setup, which matters when you\'re deploying multiple tables and benches against a tight load-in window.","Coordinates with cross back chairs for flexible seating arrangements. Pairs directly with the Sonoma Cross Back Chair for mixed bench-and-chair configurations at the same table, giving rental operators and venues flexibility to accommodate different guest preferences at the same setup."]', 'specifications' => '{"Special Order Item":"No","Can ship FedEx?":"Yes","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Overall Length \\/ Depth":"96\'\'","Overall Height":"17\'\'","Overall Width":"12\'\'","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Item Weight":"34 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[{"question":"How many people does this bench seat?","answer":"At 96\\" long and 12\\" wide, the bench comfortably seats 4 to 5 guests per side. Two benches per table covers a full 8-foot farm table setup for 8 to 10 guests."},{"question":"Does the bench fold for storage and transport?","answer":"Yes. The bench folds flat, reducing its footprint significantly for warehouse storage and trailer loading. No tools or assembly required \\u2014 unfold and it\'s ready to use."},{"question":"Can this bench be used outdoors?","answer":"Yes, for events on level outdoor surfaces. As with any wood-finish event furniture, storing the bench indoors between events and avoiding prolonged moisture exposure will extend its lifespan and preserve the finish over a rental or venue season."}]', 'default_color' => 'Rustic', 'color_variants' => '[{"label":"Fruitwood with Black Grain","swatch":"#47260c","gallery":["images\\/products\\/sonoma-folding-farm-t