            ['id' => 137, 'product_category_id' => 4, 'name' => 'Premium Double-Braced Steel Folding Chair - Grey', 'slug' => 'premium-double-braced-steel-folding-chair-grey', 'sku' => 'MFC2GRY-V2', 'brand' => 'Titan Event Furniture™', 'price' => 16.99, 'stock' => 100, 'image' => 'images/products/premium-double-braced-steel-folding-chair-grey/bac02fbecff3.jpg', 'gallery' => '["images\\/products\\/premium-double-braced-steel-folding-chair-grey\\/bac02fbecff3.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-double-braced-steel-folding-chair-grey\\/b2fd1ff42ffd.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-double-braced-steel-folding-chair-grey\\/bdada835088b.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-double-braced-steel-folding-chair-grey\\/849b28434577.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-double-braced-steel-folding-chair-grey\\/60e3da7cd8fa.jpg"]', 'description' => 'The Titan Series Steel Folding Chair offers a dependable, no-nonsense seating solution designed for strength, practicality, and everyday use.', 'features' => '["The Titan Series Steel Folding Chair offers a dependable, no-nonsense seating solution designed for strength, practicality, and everyday use.","Constructed with a heavy-duty steel frame and a double bracing system, it delivers excellent stability while remaining lightweight and easy to handle.","The smooth, contoured steel seat and back provide lasting comfort and are easy to clean, making this chair ideal for high-turnover environments.","Perfect for events, schools, meeting spaces, and rental operations, this chair is built to withstand frequent use while maintaining a clean, professional appearance.","The foldable design allows for efficient storage and quick setup, making it a smart, durable choice for any setting where reliability matters."]', 'specifications' => '{"UPC":"810171062505","Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k, Free Shipping on 50 or more","Can ship FedEx?":"Yes","Country of Manufacture":"China","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Color":"Gray","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Frame":"Steel","Overall Height":"30\'\'","Overall Width":"18.25\'\'","Overall Length \\/ Depth":"29.5\'\'","Seat Color":"Grey","Seat Size":"16\'\' x 16\'\'","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Stackable?":"Yes","Has Arms":"No","Item Weight":"9 lbs.","Static Weight Capacity":"500 lbs.","Dynamic Weight Capacity":"300 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[]', 'default_color' => NULL, 'color_variants' => '[]', 'is_active' => 1, 'created_at' => '2026-06-18 08:17:10', 'updated_at' => '2026-06-18 08:38:17'],
            ['id' => 138, 'product_category_id' => 4, 'name' => 'Premium Triple-Braced Fabric Padded Metal Folding Chair - Black', 'slug' => 'premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black', 'sku' => 'MFC2BKFP', 'brand' => 'Titan Event Furniture™', 'price' => 32.99, 'stock' => 100, 'image' => 'images/products/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black/1b824c0e998d.jpg', 'gallery' => '["images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/1b824c0e998d.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/d3e405381ff5.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/3c977db8e477.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/078448d9ba6e.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/62a4a0f8a4d9.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/a862ad7bac7f.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/3cedddc7cf2c.jpg"]', 'description' => 'A commercial-grade fabric padded metal folding chair built for conference centers, hotels, churches, and event operations that need comfort alongside high-frequency durability.', 'features' => '["A commercial-grade fabric padded metal folding chair built for conference centers, hotels, churches, and event operations that need comfort alongside high-frequency durability.","An 18-gauge powder-coated steel frame with triple U-bracing, quad hinges, and a 500 lb. static weight capacity provides the structural foundation, while a fabric padded seat and backrest deliver a softer, warmer seating experience than vinyl for guests at extended events.","Commercial-grade chairs","Rugged 18 gauge steel frame","Cushioned Seat and Backrest","Fabric-Upholstered Seat and Back","Powder-coated frame","Party Rental Tested!","Fabric upholstery delivers a softer, warmer seated experience than vinyl. Particularly well suited for air-conditioned conference rooms and multi-hour events where vinyl can feel cold and hard, fabric padding provides a more comfortable contact surface for guests seated over extended periods.","Triple U-bracing and quad hinges maintain structural integrity through heavy use. Three reinforcement points across the back frame and four-point hinge construction keep the chair tight and stable through thousands of setups, preventing the flex and hinge wear that causes lesser folding chairs to loosen over time.","Multiple color options coordinate with your venue or facility. Available fabric colors let conference centers, hotels, and churches match existing d\\u00e9cor or establish a consistent look across a full chair inventory without relying on chair covers.","At 12.75 lbs., setup and breakdown stay manageable at scale. Lighter than most commercial padded folding chairs at this construction level, the weight advantage compounds across large event setups where crew time and physical effort add up quickly.","Non-marring floor glides protect finished floors at every event. Built-in floor glides on all four leg feet prevent scratching on hardwood, vinyl, polished concrete, and other finished surfaces, reducing floor repair costs and facility complaints over the life of your inventory."]', 'specifications' => '{"Special Order Item":"No","Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k, Free Shipping on 50 or more","Can ship FedEx?":"Yes","Country of Manufacture":"China","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Material":"Steel","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Frame":"Steel","Folded Dimensions":"38\\u201d H x 18.5\\u201d W x 3.75\\u201d D","Padded Seat":"Yes","Overall Height":"29.75\'\'","Overall Width":"18.5\'\'","Overall Length \\/ Depth":"19\'\' D","Seat Material":"Fabric","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Stackable?":"Yes","Has Arms":"No","Product Warranty":"3 Year Warranty","Item Weight":"12.75 lbs","Static Weight Capacity":"500 lbs.","Dynamic Weight Capacity":"300 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[{"question":"How much weight can each chair hold?","answer":"All of our metal folding chairs are commercial-grade quality with a weight capacity of 500 pounds."},{"question":"Is there a warranty for Metal Folding Chairs?","answer":"Yes, we offer a 3 year product warranty on all of our Steel Folding Chairs."},{"question":"Do the chairs ship assembled?","answer":"Yes, all of our Metal Folding Chairs ship assembled."},{"question":"Will these Chairs rust?","answer":"Our Metal Folding Chair frames are powder coated to insure that the frame will not rust."},{"question":"Are Metal Folding Chairs CA117 Rated?","answer":"Yes, our chairs are CA117 rated. For more information, please visit www.p65warnings.ca.gov."}]', 'default_color' => 'Black', 'color_variants' => '[{"label":"Black","swatch":"images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/d889c95969e0.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/3cedddc7cf2c.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/f4525d2a9142.png","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/096ac87a87ed.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/1ec4c0fcdc9d.png"]},{"label":"Beige","swatch":"images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/9c3f2086451c.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/c649ba702a74.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/58d1a22cc5e0.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/c101f95537a3.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/1257b7752cf2.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/d3cabd41fbdb.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/98c77a338392.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/7f74abc930d0.jpg"]},{"label":"Gray\\/Navy","swatch":"images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/c1d9e440ec4b.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/7390e8e34177.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/938e58a6e370.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/4955676cb6ba.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/99e5d749b1e7.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/1f637f695cad.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/3ec73169cc17.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/c3ccaa05876f.jpg"]},{"label":"Navy","swatch":"images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/d649351d4919.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/10858f8f1ca7.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/badf8eb052ac.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/7f98987a9ab9.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/0f4c374c7fd6.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/d2a6be860a70.jpg","images\\/products\\/premium-triple-braced-fabric-padded-metal-folding-chair-black\\/04c6a06b0055.jpg","images\\/products\\/p