"Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k, Free Shipping on 50 or more","Can ship FedEx?":"Yes","Country of Manufacture":"China","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Material":"Resin","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Folded Dimensions":"17.5\'\' x 35\'\' x 2.19\'\'","Padded Seat":"Yes","Overall Height":"31\'\'","Overall Width":"17.5\'\'","Overall Length \\/ Depth":"20\'\'","Footprint":"17.5\'\' x 20\'\'","Seat Height":"17.5\'\'","Seat Size":"15.5\'\' x 14\'\'","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Stackable?":"Yes","Has Arms":"No","Product Warranty":"3 Year Warranty","Static Weight Capacity":"1102 lbs.","Dynamic Weight Capacity":"353 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[{"question":"What is the weight capacity of Resin Folding Chairs?","answer":"These chairs have been independently tested by SGS laboratories to hold in excess of 1000+ lbs static weight."},{"question":"Can I stack Resin Folding Chairs?","answer":"Yes, our customers typically stack resin folding chairs 25 high. Check out our Folding Chair Dolly so you can better move them from Point A to B."},{"question":"Is the cushion removable?","answer":"Yes, we sell replacement cushions. Please visit Replacement Cushion for Resin Folding Chairs."},{"question":"What are Resin Folding Chairs made of?","answer":"Our Resin folding chairs are made from high-density polypropylene, which are durable, lightweight plastics that are resistant to weather, stains, and scratches."},{"question":"Are Resin Folding Chairs suitable for outdoor use?","answer":"Yes, our Resin Folding Chairs are designed to withstand outdoor conditions. They are resistant to UV rays, moisture, and temperature changes, making them ideal for events, weddings, and outdoor gatherings."},{"question":"How do I clean Resin Folding Chairs?","answer":"To clean Resin Folding Chairs, wipe them down with a mild soap and water solution. For tougher stains, use a soft brush. Rinse thoroughly and let them air dry."}]', 'default_color' => 'White', 'color_variants' => '[{"label":"Brown w\\/ Ivory Pad","swatch":"#85522b","gallery":["images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/8dcf8114178f.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/a0d6af5c3962.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/ba21e763c863.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/b6ac51a41789.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/5e22d88271fd.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/82e03ff5a9b0.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/1f9e50da51b0.jpeg"]},{"label":"Dark Brown w\\/ Ivory Pad","swatch":"#361d0a","gallery":["images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/cb6af739586b.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/caf36e7f437e.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/a9a946fba05e.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/2b1a819605d3.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/5a74998050b4.jpeg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/fb716ecaa594.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/dcfe5d365775.jpg"]},{"label":"Black","swatch":"images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/d889c95969e0.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/077ee8391465.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/fddeca19b4cf.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/20164f7079a8.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/0be4d2529ea1.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/608842727a13.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/30f526253ccd.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/8399ad06dc83.jpg"]},{"label":"Mahogany","swatch":"images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/282fc36664b4.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/923643582888.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/175e209e4a49.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/118ac7e6a941.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/c9eb049793b4.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/26299ffe4947.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/95320591feaa.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/ba6956922283.jpg"]},{"label":"White","swatch":"#ffffff","gallery":["images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/b8f89b0feb78.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/1b5d8cdc72c0.jpeg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/8ffd4a4c675f.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/4499f73f89fe.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/e51dce5accb7.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/3db80c3012f6.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/390c0593a44e.jpg"]},{"label":"Green","swatch":"images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/6dc0555384cf.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/b8f89b0feb78.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/1b5d8cdc72c0.jpeg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/8ffd4a4c675f.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/4499f73f89fe.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/e51dce5accb7.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/3db80c3012f6.jpg","images\\/products\\/white-resin-folding-chair\\/390c0593a44e.jpg"]}]', 'is_active' => 1, 'created_at' => '2026-06-18 08:27:52', 'updated_at' => '2026-06-18 08:38:17'],
            ['id' => 174, 'product_category_id' => 6, 'name' => 'TimberTouch ™ Resin Folding Chair - Natural with White Pad', 'slug' => 'timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad', 'sku' => 'RFC4NTWP', 'brand' => 'Titan Event Furniture™', 'price' => 37.99, 'stock' => 100, 'image' => 'images/products/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad/0809f0951286.jpg', 'gallery' => '["images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/0809f0951286.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/af18d71be04a.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/f4740e115896.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/083ab37dc6e3.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/96009c68f7a5.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/06ff639f9068.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/80f871ccbe62.jpg"]', 'description' => 'The TimberTouch™ resin folding chair brings the warmth of a wood grain aesthetic to commercial-grade resin construction, making it a practical choice for wedding venues, event rental companies, and hospitality operations that want a more elevated look without the maintenance demands of real wood.', 'features' => '["The TimberTouch\\u2122 resin folding chair brings the warmth of a wood grain aesthetic to commercial-grade resin construction, making it a practical choice for wedding venues, event rental companies, and hospitality operations that want a more elevated look without the maintenance demands of real wood.","Built on the same commercial-grade frame platform as the TitanPRO\\u2122 series, it includes a padded seat for added guest comfort, folds flat for easy storage and transport, and handles both indoor and outdoor use without fading or degrading.","Delivers a wood aesthetic without the wood upkeep. The UV-resistant, waterproof wood grain finish holds its appearance through outdoor events, repeated cleaning, and regular commercial use, with no refinishing, sealing, or special storage required.","Padded seat improves guest comfort at longer events. Unlike standard hard-shell resin folding chairs, the built-in padded seat makes these chairs well suited for seated dinners, wedding ceremonies, and multi-hour events where guest comfort directly reflects on your venue or rental business.","Handles outdoor and indoor events without performance tradeoffs. Weather-resistant resin construction and a UV-treated finish mean these chairs can move between outdoor ceremonies and indoor receptions without fading, degrading, or requiring separate storage protocols.","Folds flat and stacks for efficient storage and fast transport. At 10 lbs. per chair, they are light enough for quick turnarounds, and the folding frame reduces the footprint in a warehouse or cargo area significantly between events.","Backed by a 3-year commercial warranty on a proven platform. Built on the same commercial-grade frame used across the TitanPRO\\u2122 line, these chairs are designed for the frequency and load of professional rental and venue use, with warranty coverage that reflects it."]', 'specifications' => '{"Special Order Item":"No","Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k, Free Shipping on 50 or more","Can ship FedEx?":"Yes","Country of Manufacture":"China","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Material":"Resin","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Padded Seat":"Yes","Overall Height":"31\'\'","Overall Width":"17.5\'\'","Overall Length \\/ Depth":"20\'\'","Recommended Seating":"1","Seat Height":"17.5\'\'","Seat Size":"15.\'5\'\' x 14\'\'","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Stackable?":"Yes","Has Arms":"No","Product Warranty":"3 Year Warranty","Item Weight":"10 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[{"question":"What makes the TimberTouch\\u2122 different from a standard resin folding chair?","answer":"The defining difference is the wood grain finish. Most commercial resin folding chairs come in plain white or black, which works fine for utility use but can look stark at weddings, rustic outdoor events, or any setting where aesthetics matter to the client. The TimberTouch\\u2122 gives those events a warmer, more natural look without introducing the maintenance requirements of real wood."},{"question":"Can these chairs be used outdoors?","answer":"Yes. The resin construction and UV-treated finish are designed for outdoor use. The surface resists sun exposure without fading and handles moisture without warping or degrading. As with any event chair, storing them indoors between events will extend their lifespan."},{"question":"Is the wood grain finish real wood?","answer":"No. The finish is a textured resin surface designed to replicate the appearance of wood grain. It is waterproof, UV resistant, and will not crack, split, or require refinishing the way real wood does. For operations that want the aesthetic of a wood chair with the durability and low maintenance of resin, that is the practical advantage of this construction."},{"question":"How do these chairs stack and store?","answer":"The TimberTouch\\u2122 folds flat and stacks for storage and transport. At 10 lbs. per chair, they are manageable for quick event setups and teardowns. For operations moving large quantities, EventStable carries a selection of folding chair dollies designed for efficient bulk transport."}]', 'default_color' => 'Natural', 'color_variants' => '[{"label":"Dark Walnut","swatch":"images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/f99d22291756.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/f532e188967a.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/13716460aa61.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/24adc26b4980.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/70b48018d15b.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/f8e466c82398.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/71b1c3537662.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/7739d58a87cb.jpg"]},{"label":"Walnut","swatch":"images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/6939177ebf47.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/956f9bd40d7d.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/83bc5bfc6253.png","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/39090b32235b.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/43cfc590c8e9.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/d0371acac70f.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/0ccc20012178.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/7562ab3e9d0c.jpg"]},{"label":"Natural","swatch":"images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/515ba0e67b95.jpg","gallery":["images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/0809f0951286.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/af18d71be04a.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/f4740e115896.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/083ab37dc6e3.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/96009c68f7a5.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/06ff639f9068.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/80f871ccbe62.jpg"]},{"label":"Light Natural","swatch":"images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/eb88eb743018.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/25e1a97e385c.png","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/06ff639f9068.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/80f871ccbe62.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/1d72ff136f76.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-natural-with-white-pad\\/bc1755098799.png"]}]', 'is_active' => 1, 'created_at' => '2026-06-18 08:28:12', 'updated_at' => '2026-06-18 08:38:17'],
