            ['id' => 176, 'product_category_id' => 6, 'name' => 'TimberTouch™ Resin Folding Chair - Walnut with Ivory Pad', 'slug' => 'timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad', 'sku' => 'RFC4WLIP', 'brand' => 'Titan Event Furniture™', 'price' => 37.99, 'stock' => 100, 'image' => 'images/products/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad/956f9bd40d7d.jpg', 'gallery' => '["images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/956f9bd40d7d.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/83bc5bfc6253.png","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/39090b32235b.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/43cfc590c8e9.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/d0371acac70f.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/0ccc20012178.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/7562ab3e9d0c.jpg"]', 'description' => 'The TimberTouch™ resin folding chair brings the warmth of a wood grain aesthetic to commercial-grade resin construction, making it a practical choice for wedding venues, event rental companies, and hospitality operations that want a more elevated look without the maintenance demands of real wood.', 'features' => '["The TimberTouch\\u2122 resin folding chair brings the warmth of a wood grain aesthetic to commercial-grade resin construction, making it a practical choice for wedding venues, event rental companies, and hospitality operations that want a more elevated look without the maintenance demands of real wood.","Built on the same commercial-grade frame platform as the TitanPRO\\u2122 series, it includes a padded seat for added guest comfort, folds flat for easy storage and transport, and handles both indoor and outdoor use without fading or degrading.","Delivers a wood aesthetic without the wood upkeep. The UV-resistant, waterproof wood grain finish holds its appearance through outdoor events, repeated cleaning, and regular commercial use, with no refinishing, sealing, or special storage required.","Padded seat improves guest comfort at longer events. Unlike standard hard-shell resin folding chairs, the built-in padded seat makes these chairs well suited for seated dinners, wedding ceremonies, and multi-hour events where guest comfort directly reflects on your venue or rental business.","Handles outdoor and indoor events without performance tradeoffs. Weather-resistant resin construction and a UV-treated finish mean these chairs can move between outdoor ceremonies and indoor receptions without fading, degrading, or requiring separate storage protocols.","Folds flat and stacks for efficient storage and fast transport. At 10 lbs. per chair, they are light enough for quick turnarounds, and the folding frame reduces the footprint in a warehouse or cargo area significantly between events.","Backed by a 3-year commercial warranty on a proven platform. Built on the same commercial-grade frame used across the TitanPRO\\u2122 line, these chairs are designed for the frequency and load of professional rental and venue use, with warranty coverage that reflects it."]', 'specifications' => '{"Special Order Item":"No","Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k, Free Shipping on 50 or more","Can ship FedEx?":"Yes","Country of Manufacture":"China","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Material":"Resin","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Padded Seat":"Yes","Overall Height":"31\'\'","Overall Width":"17.5\'\'","Overall Length \\/ Depth":"20\'\'","Recommended Seating":"1","Seat Height":"17.5\'\'","Seat Size":"15.\'5\'\' x 14\'\'","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Stackable?":"Yes","Has Arms":"No","Product Warranty":"3 Year Warranty","Item Weight":"10 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[{"question":"What makes the TimberTouch\\u2122 different from a standard resin folding chair?","answer":"The defining difference is the wood grain finish. Most commercial resin folding chairs come in plain white or black, which works fine for utility use but can look stark at weddings, rustic outdoor events, or any setting where aesthetics matter to the client. The TimberTouch\\u2122 gives those events a warmer, more natural look without introducing the maintenance requirements of real wood."},{"question":"Can these chairs be used outdoors?","answer":"Yes. The resin construction and UV-treated finish are designed for outdoor use. The surface resists sun exposure without fading and handles moisture without warping or degrading. As with any event chair, storing them indoors between events will extend their lifespan."},{"question":"Is the wood grain finish real wood?","answer":"No. The finish is a textured resin surface designed to replicate the appearance of wood grain. It is waterproof, UV resistant, and will not crack, split, or require refinishing the way real wood does. For operations that want the aesthetic of a wood chair with the durability and low maintenance of resin, that is the practical advantage of this construction."},{"question":"How do these chairs stack and store?","answer":"The TimberTouch\\u2122 folds flat and stacks for storage and transport. At 10 lbs. per chair, they are manageable for quick event setups and teardowns. For operations moving large quantities, EventStable carries a selection of folding chair dollies designed for efficient bulk transport."}]', 'default_color' => 'Walnut', 'color_variants' => '[{"label":"Dark Walnut","swatch":"images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/f99d22291756.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/f532e188967a.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/13716460aa61.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/24adc26b4980.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/70b48018d15b.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/f8e466c82398.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/71b1c3537662.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/7739d58a87cb.jpg"]},{"label":"Walnut","swatch":"images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/6939177ebf47.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/956f9bd40d7d.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/83bc5bfc6253.png","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/39090b32235b.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/43cfc590c8e9.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/d0371acac70f.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/0ccc20012178.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/7562ab3e9d0c.jpg"]},{"label":"Natural","swatch":"images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/515ba0e67b95.jpg","gallery":["images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/0809f0951286.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/af18d71be04a.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/f4740e115896.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/083ab37dc6e3.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/96009c68f7a5.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/06ff639f9068.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/80f871ccbe62.jpg"]},{"label":"Light Natural","swatch":"images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/eb88eb743018.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/25e1a97e385c.png","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/06ff639f9068.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/80f871ccbe62.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/1d72ff136f76.jpg","images\\/products\\/timbertouch-resin-folding-chair-walnut-with-ivory-pad\\/bc1755098799.png"]}]', 'is_active' => 1, 'created_at' => '2026-06-18 08:28:34', 'updated_at' => '2026-06-18 08:38:17'],
            ['id' => 177, 'product_category_id' => 6, 'name' => 'Green Resin Folding Chair', 'slug' => 'green-resin-folding-chair', 'sku' => 'RFC6GR', 'brand' => 'Titan Event Furniture™', 'price' => 35.49, 'stock' => 100, 'image' => 'images/products/green-resin-folding-chair/cb2fe7e4e016.jpg', 'gallery' => '["images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/cb2fe7e4e016.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/9cddf2f24c3f.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/3c2a4841cbf9.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/4eda08483879.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/9670ef0ee816.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/30900ad7a5f9.png","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/8998105b5a83.jpg"]', 'description' => 'Resin Folding Chairs are the ideal choice for padded wedding chairs and the standard for garden folding chairs.', 'features' => '["Resin Folding Chairs are the ideal choice for padded wedding chairs and the standard for garden folding chairs.","UV protected. lightweight and easy to maintain.","Suitable for indoor and outdoor use.","Our wholesale resin folding chairs are a perfect fit for almost any application.","Perhaps the most popular padded wedding chair, they have become the standard for garden folding chairs, as they are made to look identical to traditional wood folding chairs.","Same weight and dimensions, but these chairs are stronger than any wood chair and will last through years of tough use.","The resin material is 100% virgin polypropylene with UV protectants included in the molding process.","This ensures the chairs will not fade or lose their bright appearance over time.","These chairs are incredibly easy to clean and maintain, as they can be wiped off with a damp rag in between rentals or events.","Resin folding chairs can be used indoors or outdoors in an any weather without fear of moisture issues.","Simply a beautiful chair, the aesthetics are enhanced with color-matching bolt covers.","Replacement covers available.","Event setups are quick and easy with resin folding chairs.","Each chair weighs only 10.5 lbs, so several can be carried at one time.","Unfold the seat and notice that the locking seat snaps into place for the stability and safety of your clients or guests.","These chairs feature a removable \\u00bd\\u2019\\u2019 vinyl padded seat cushion which is comfortable and supported by the seat frame and seat bar.","Further easing ownership over the life of the chairs, the cushion can be removed for repair.","Don\\u2019t want to repair your cushions?","No worries - we\\u2019ve got you covered on replacements as well: replacement cushions.","Resin folding chairs have a built-in nesting design that allow the chairs to stack amazingly straight up and down.","Adding to that, the chairs resist sliding off one another making moving them around a breeze.","Generally our customers will make stacks 25 high.","25 is an easy number for counting and makes for a very manageable stack for transport, whether on a cart or dolly.","However, for storage, these chairs can be stacked as high as you are comfortable with.","We know that weight capacity is important to our commercial customers.","Our chairs have been independently certified by SGS Laboratories to hold in excess of 1000 lbs.","The chairs and cushions have also been tested and found to meet the requirements of CA TB 133 (stricter than CA117).","These chairs have been party rental proven in our very own event rental company to be tough, durable, reliable, easy to transport, a great investment and popular with our clients.","Check out our buyer\'s guide for 10 reasons to choose resin folding chairs or our Ultimate Folding Chairs Buyer\'s Guide for more information."]', 'specifications' => '{"Special Order Item":"No","Dimensions":"Height: 31\\" Width: 17.5\\" Seat Width: 15.5\\" Seat Depth: 14\\" Seat Height: 17.5\\" Folded Length: 35\\" Folded Thickness: 2.25\\" Weight: 10 lbs","Free Shipping Deal Type":"Free Shipping on Tables and Chairs Over $5k, Free Shipping on 50 or more","Can ship FedEx?":"Yes","Country of Manufacture":"China","Brand":"Titan Event Furniture\\u2122","Material":"Resin","Commercial-Grade?":"Yes","Folded Dimensions":"17.5\'\' x 35\'\' x 2.19\'\'","Padded Seat":"Yes","Overall Height":"31\'\'","Overall Width":"17.5\'\'","Overall Length \\/ Depth":"20\'\'","Footprint":"17.5\'\' x 20\'\'","Seat Height":"17.5\'\'","Seat Size":"15.5\'\' x 14\'\'","Ships Assembled?":"Yes","Stackable?":"Yes","Has Arms":"No","Product Warranty":"3 Year Warranty","Static Weight Capacity":"1102 lbs.","Dynamic Weight Capacity":"353 lbs.","California Residents":"Click here for Proposition 65 warning"}', 'faq' => '[{"question":"What is the weight capacity of Resin Folding Chairs?","answer":"These chairs have been independently tested by SGS laboratories to hold in excess of 1000+ lbs static weight."},{"question":"Can I stack Resin Folding Chairs?","answer":"Yes, our customers typically stack resin folding chairs 25 high. Check out our Folding Chair Dolly so you can better move them from Point A to B."},{"question":"Is the cushion removable?","answer":"Yes, we sell replacement cushions. Please visit Replacement Cushion for Resin Folding Chairs."},{"question":"What are Resin Folding Chairs made of?","answer":"Our Resin folding chairs are made from high-density polypropylene, which are durable, lightweight plastics that are resistant to weather, stains, and scratches."},{"question":"Are Resin Folding Chairs suitable for outdoor use?","answer":"Yes, our Resin Folding Chairs are designed to withstand outdoor conditions. They are resistant to UV rays, moisture, and temperature changes, making them ideal for events, weddings, and outdoor gatherings."},{"question":"How do I clean Resin Folding Chairs?","answer":"To clean Resin Folding Chairs, wipe them down with a mild soap and water solution. For tougher stains, use a soft brush. Rinse thoroughly and let them air dry."}]', 'default_color' => 'Green', 'color_variants' => '[{"label":"Brown w\\/ Ivory Pad","swatch":"#85522b","gallery":["images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/8dcf8114178f.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/a0d6af5c3962.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/ba21e763c863.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/b6ac51a41789.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/5e22d88271fd.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/82e03ff5a9b0.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/1f9e50da51b0.jpeg"]},{"label":"Dark Brown w\\/ Ivory Pad","swatch":"#361d0a","gallery":["images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/cb6af739586b.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/caf36e7f437e.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/a9a946fba05e.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/2b1a819605d3.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/5a74998050b4.jpeg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/fb716ecaa594.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/dcfe5d365775.jpg"]},{"label":"Black","swatch":"images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/d889c95969e0.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/077ee8391465.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/fddeca19b4cf.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/20164f7079a8.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/0be4d2529ea1.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/608842727a13.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/30f526253ccd.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/8399ad06dc83.jpg"]},{"label":"Mahogany","swatch":"images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/282fc36664b4.png","gallery":["images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/923643582888.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\\/175e209e4a49.jpg","images\\/products\\/green-resin-folding-chair\